stency with less or zero variations which matters the most in branding. All in all, getting lots of wholesale chocolate boxes with ribbon is a win-win for everyone!</p>8:["$","section",null,{"className":"sm:max-w-8xl max-w-[95%] mx-auto py-8","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-linear-to-br from-gray-50 via-white to-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-100","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-4 mb-6","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"w-1 h-12 bg-linear-to-b from-[#EE334B] to-[#213554] rounded-full"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-[#213554]","children":["Learn More About "," Chocolate Box with Ribbon"]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"pt-2","children":["$","div",null,{"className":" text-gray-700  banner-content-wrapper leading-relaxed","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$13"},"style":{"lineHeight":"1.75"}}]}]]}]}]
